#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:3055(para) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:258(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:258(para)
msgid ""
"SMTP AUTH configuration is complete. Now it is time to start and test the "
"setup. You can run the following command to start the SASL daemon: "
"<screen><command>sudo /etc/init.d/saslauthd start</command></screen> To see "
"if SMTP-AUTH and TLS work properly, run the following command: "
"<screen><command>telnet mail.example.com 25</command></screen> After you "
"have established the connection to the postfix mail server, type: "
"<screen>ehlo mail.example.com</screen> If you see the following lines among "
"others, then everything is working perfectly. Type <command>quit</command> "
"to exit. <placeholder-1/>"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurationen för SMTP AUTH är färdig. Nu är det dags att starta och testa "
"din installation. Du kan köra följande kommando för att starta SASL-demonen: "
"<screen><command>sudo /etc/init.d/saslauthd start</command></screen> För att "
"se om SMTP-AUTH och TLS fungerar som det ska kan du köra följande kommando: "
"<screen><command>telnet mail.exempel.com 25</command></screen> När du har "
"blivit ansluten till postfixservern, skriv: <screen>ehlo "
"mail.example.com</screen> Om du bland annat ser följande rader fungerar allt "
"som det ska. Skriv <command>quit</command> för att avsluta. <placeholder-1/>"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:3079(title) ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:3321(title) ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:3388(title) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:282(title) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:527(title) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:594(title) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:282(title) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:527(title) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:594(title)
msgid "Exim4"
msgstr "Exim4"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:3080(para) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:283(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:283(para)
msgid ""
"<application>Exim4</application> is another Message Transfer Agent (MTA) "
"developed at the University of Cambridge for use on Unix systems connected "
"to the internet. Exim can be installed in place of "
"<application>sendmail</application>, although the configuration of "
"<application>exim</application> is quite different to that of "
"<application>sendmail</application>."
msgstr ""
"<application>Exim4</application> är en annan Message Transfer Agent (MTA) "
"utvecklad på University of Cambridge för att användas på Unix system "
"kopplade till internet. Exim kan installeras istället för "
"<application>sendmail</application>, fastän konfigurationen av "
"<application>exim</application> är ganska olik den i "
"<application>sendmail</application>."

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:3091(para) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:294(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:294(para)
msgid ""
"To install <application>exim4</application>, run the following command: "
"<screen>\n"
"<command>sudo apt-get install exim4 exim4-base exim4-config</command>\n"
"</screen>"
msgstr ""
"Kör följande kommando för att installera <application>exim4</application>: "
"<screen>\n"
"<command>sudo apt-get install exim4 exim4-base exim4-config</command>\n"
"</screen>"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:3100(para) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:303(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:303(para)
msgid ""
"To configure <application>exim4</application>, run the following command: "
"<screen>\n"
"<command>sudo dpkg-reconfigure exim4-config</command>\n"
"</screen> The user interface will be displayed. The user interface lets you "
"configure many parameters. For example, In <application>exim4</application> "
"the configuration files are split among multiple files. If you wish to have "
"them in one file you can configure accordingly in this user interface."
msgstr ""
"Kör följande kommando för att konfigurera <application>exim4</application>: "
"<screen>\n"
"<command>sudo dpkg-reconfigure exim4-config</command>\n"
"</screen> Användargränssnittet kommer visas, som låter dig konfigurera många "
"parametrar. Till exempel är konfigurationsfilerna för "
"<application>exim4</application> uppdelade i många filer. Om du vill ha alla "
"i samma fil kan du välja det i användargränssnittet."

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:3129(para) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:332(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:332(para)
msgid ""
"At any time, you should not edit the master configuration file, "
"<filename>/var/lib/exim4/config.autogenerated</filename> manually. It is "
"updated automatically every time you run <command>update-exim4.conf</command>"
msgstr ""
"Du bör aldrig ändra i huvudkonfigurationsfilen "
"<filename>/var/lib/exim4/config.autogenerated</filename> själv. Den "
"uppdateras automatiskt varje gång du kör <command>update-exim4.conf</command>"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:3112(para) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:315(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:315(para)
msgid ""
"All the parameters you configure in the user interface are stored in "
"<filename>/etc/exim4/update-exim4.conf.conf</filename> file. If you wish to "
"re-configure, either you re-run the configuration wizard or manually edit "
"this file using your favourite editor. Once you configure, you can run the "
"following command to generate the master configuration file: <screen>\n"
"<command>sudo update-exim4.conf</command>\n"
"</screen> The master configuration file, is generated and it is stored in "
"<filename>/var/lib/exim4/config.autogenerated</filename>. <placeholder-1/> "
"You can run the following command to start <application>exim4</application> "
"daemon. <screen>\n"
"<command>sudo /etc/init.d/exim4 start</command>\n"
"</screen><emphasis role=\"strong\">TODO:</emphasis> This section should "
"cover configuring SMTP AUTH with exim4."
msgstr ""
"Alla parametrar du konfigurerar i användargränssnittet sparas i filen "
"<filename>/etc/exim4/update-exim4.conf.conf</filename>. Om du vill "
"omkonfigurera så kan du antingen köra konfigurationsguiden eller manuellt "
"redigera filen med din favorit editor. Efter du har redigerat filen kan du "
"köra följande kommando för att skapa master-konfigurationsfilen: <screen>\n"
"<command>sudo update-exim4.conf</command>\n"
"</screen> Master-konfigurationsfilen skapas och sparas i "
"<filename>/var/lib/exim4/config.autogenerated</filename>. <placeholder-1/> "
"Du kan köra följande kommando för att starta "
"<application>exim4</application> daemon. <screen>\n"
"<command>sudo /etc/init.d/exim4 start</command>\n"
"</screen><emphasis role=\"strong\">TODO:</emphasis> Det här avsnittet skall "
"omfatta konfigureringen av SMTP AUTH med exim4."

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:3149(title) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:352(title) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:352(title)
msgid "Dovecot Server"
msgstr "Dovecot-server"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:3150(para) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:353(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:353(para)
msgid ""
"<application>Dovecot</application> is a Mail Delivery Agent, written with "
"security primarily in mind. It supports the major mailbox formats: mbox or "
"Maildir. This section explain how to set it up as an imap or pop3 server."
msgstr ""
"<application>Dovecot</application> är en Mail Delivery Agent som är skriven "
"med största fokus på säkerhet. Den stöder de vanligaste mailbox-formaten: "
"mbox och maildir. Den här avdelningen förklarar hur du ställer in det för "
"att bli en imap- eller pop3-server."

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:3158(para) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:361(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:361(para)
msgid ""
"To install <application>dovecot</application>, run the following command in "
"the command prompt: <screen>\n"
"<command>sudo apt-get install dovecot-common dovecot-imapd dovecot-"
"pop3d</command>\n"
"</screen>"
msgstr ""
"Kör följande kommando i en terminalprompt för att installera "
"<application>dovecot</application>:\n"
"<screen>\n"
"<command>sudo apt-get install dovecot-common dovecot-imapd dovecot-"
"pop3d</command>\n"
"</screen>"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:3168(para) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:371(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:371(para)
msgid ""
"To configure <application>dovecot</application>, you can edit the file "
"<filename>/etc/dovecot/dovecot.conf</filename>. You can choose the protocol "
"you use. It could be pop3, pop3s (pop3 secure), imap and imaps (imap "
"secure). A description of these protocols is beyond the scope of this guide. "
"For further information, refer to the wikipedia articles on <ulink "
"url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/POP3\">POP3</ulink> and <ulink "
"url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internet_Message_Access_Protocol\">IMAP</u"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"För att konfigurera <application>dovecot</application> kan du ändra på filen "
"<filename>/etc/dovecot/dovecot.conf</filename>. Du kan välja vilket "
"protokoll du vill använda. Det kan vara pop3, pop3s (säker pop3), imap och "
"imaps (säker imap). Den här guiden kommer inte att ta upp skillnaden på "
"dessa protokoll. För mer information, läs wikipediaartiklarna om <ulink "
"url=\"http://sv.wikipedia.org/wiki/POP3\">POP3</ulink> och <ulink "
"url=\"http://sv.wikipedia.org/wiki/IMAP\">IMAP</ulink>."

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:3183(programlisting) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:386(programlisting) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:386(programlisting)
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"protocols = pop3 pop3s imap imaps\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"protocols = pop3 pop3s imap imaps\n"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:3188(programlisting) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:391(programlisting) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:391(programlisting)
